                     <interp inst="t17840707-23-person300" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            .)</p>
               <p>- CLEVELEY sworn.</p>
               <p>Deposed that he saw the prisoner take the prosecutor's handkerchief, and he was immediately pursued and taken.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I have no witnesses nor friends.</p>
